title: Saeima Member Edgars Zelderis dies
summary_full: After a long absence, Saeima MP Edgars Zelderis has died, the Saeima Press Service confirmed to the LETA news agency.
summary_public: After a long absence, Saeima MP Edgars Zelderis has died, the Saeima Press Service confirmed to the LETA news agency.
